Troubleshooting Tips
MobSF Server Won't Start:

Verify Python virtual environment is activated
Check port 8000 is not already in use: sudo lsof -i :8000
Review logs in MobSF directory for error messages
APK Upload Fails:

Ensure APK file size is under 100MB
Verify file is a valid APK (check with file command)
Check MobSF server is running and accessible
Scan Takes Too Long:

Large APKs (>50MB) may take 5-10 minutes
Check system resources (CPU, RAM) are sufficient
Consider reducing concurrent scans in batch processing
API Returns Empty Results:

Verify scan has completed before requesting results
Check file hash is correct (returned from upload)
Ensure proper API endpoint URLs are used
